===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

[[File:A lindworm.jpg|thumb]]

# {{lb|en|mythology}} A lindworm is a slithering wingless [[draconic]] creature with a serpentine body, two arms in the upper body and a dragon-like head. May have either a poisonous or fiery breath.
# {{lb|en|folklore, fairy tales, fantasy and heraldry}} Their appearance may vary, they may look either like wyverns, four-legged dragons, sea serpents or classic lindworms as in the definition above.

